<h1 class="tab-heading">Yearly Projection</h1>

<section class="kv-grid" aria-label="Headline projection">
  <div class="kv-cell">
    <span class="kv-cell__k">STARTING CAPITAL</span>
    <span class="kv-cell__v">{{ projection.starting_capital_display }}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="kv-cell">
    <span class="kv-cell__k">NOTIONAL · per trade</span>
    <span class="kv-cell__v">{{ projection.live_notional_display }}</span>
  </div>
  <div class="kv-cell">
    <span class="kv-cell__k">DIRECTIONAL · annual</span>
    <span class="kv-cell__v
                {% if projection.directional_annual > 0 %}is-up
                {% elif projection.directional_annual < 0 %}is-down{% endif %}">
      {{ projection.directional_annual_display }}
    </span>
    <span class="kv-cell__hint">{{ projection.directional_pct_display }} · momentum + whale + breakout + reversal + scalp + crossover</span>
  </div>
  <div class="kv-cell">
    <span class="kv-cell__k">PAIR-SPREAD · annual</span>
    <span class="kv-cell__v
                {% if projection.pair_annual > 0 %}is-up
                {% elif projection.pair_annual < 0 %}is-down{% endif %}">
      {{ projection.pair_annual_display }}
    </span>
    <span class="kv-cell__hint">{{ projection.pair_pct_display }} · dollar-neutral, not directly comparable</span>
  </div>
  <div class="kv-cell">
    <span class="kv-cell__k">OBSERVED · 30d annualized</span>
    <span class="kv-cell__v
                {% if projection.observed_annual > 0 %}is-up
                {% elif projection.observed_annual < 0 %}is-down{% endif %}">
      {{ projection.observed_annual_display }}
    </span>
    <span class="kv-cell__hint">
      {{ projection.observed_pct_display }} · n={{ projection.observed_n }} closed
      {% if projection.reality_check_display != "—" %}· {{ projection.reality_check_display }}{% endif %}
    </span>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="trades-table-wrap">
  <table class="trades-table projection-table" aria-label="Per-strategy projection">
    <caption class="sr-only">
      Per-strategy yearly projection scaled from backtest results to live sizing.
      Each row's annual PnL is discounted on display by sqrt(n/20) so small-sample rows don't visually dominate.
    </caption>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th scope="col">Bot</th>
        <th scope="col">Strategy</th>
        <th scope="col">Symbol</th>
        <th scope="col">TF</th>
        <th scope="col" data-sort-type="num">PF</th>
        <th scope="col" data-sort-type="num">Trades/yr</th>
        <th scope="col" data-sort-type="num">Annual %</th>
        <th scope="col" data-sort-type="num">Max DD</th>
        <th scope="col" data-sort-type="num">Window</th>
        <th scope="col">Confidence</th>
        <th scope="col" data-sort-type="num">Annual PnL</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      {% for r in projection.rows %}
      <tr class="projection-row {{ r.row_class }}">
        <td>
          <span class="bot-tag bot-tag--{{ r.bot|lower }}">{{ r.bot }}</span>
        </td>
        <td class="trades-table__strategy">{{ r.name }}</td>
        <td class="trades-table__symbol">{{ r.symbol }}</td>
        <td class="trades-table__date">{{ r.interval }}</td>
        <td class="num"
            {% if r.pf_tooltip %}title="{{ r.pf_tooltip }}"{% endif %}>
          {{ r.pf_display }}
        </td>
        <td class="num">{{ r.trades_per_year_display }}</td>
        <td class="num">{{ r.annual_pct_display }}</td>
        <td class="num">{{ r.dd_display }}</td>
        <td class="num">{{ r.window_years_display }}</td>
        <td>
          <span class="confidence-pill confidence-pill--{{ r.confidence }}"
                title="{{ r.source_note }}">
            {{ r.confidence_label }}
          </span>
        </td>
        <td class="num
                    {% if r.is_awaiting %}
                    {% elif r.annual_pnl_live > 0 %}is-up
                    {% elif r.annual_pnl_live < 0 %}is-down{% endif %}">
          {{ r.annual_pnl_live_display }}
          {% if r.sample_chip %}<small class="sample-chip">{{ r.sample_chip }}</small>{% endif %}
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endfor %}
      {% if not projection.rows %}
      <tr>
        <td colspan="11" class="trades-table__strategy" style="text-align:center; padding: var(--space-5);">
          <em>No strategies with backtest stats configured.</em>
        </td>
      </tr>
      {% endif %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>

<p class="tab-note">
  Annual PnL per row is discounted on display by
  <code>√(n/20)</code> — a row with n=5 trades shows ≈50% of its raw
  projected number; n=20+ shows the full number. The
  <strong>Observed · 30d annualized</strong> card is the reality check:
  if it's far below the modeled headline, the gap tells you which side
  to trust. PF capped at <code>>10</code> on display to avoid
  three-digit ratios; <code>∞</code> means the backtest window had no
  losses (treat as directional only). Past performance doesn't predict
  future regime.
</p>
